<!-- /sections/section-feature-plug-and-play-zero-configuration.liquid -->

<div id="section-feature-plug-and-play-zero-configuration" class="section-row {{ section.settings.color_bg }}" 
  style="--PT: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px; --PB: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;">
  <div class="{{ section.settings.width }} section-padding">

    
    <div class="text__standard" style="margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <h1 class="h2 standard__heading heading-size-6" >Plug-and-Play. Zero Configuration</h1>
      <div class="standard__rte body-size-2" >
        <p>
          Deeper connect is a truly all-in-one solution requiring minimal configuration to connect to all your devices. With the included Wi-Fi adapter, setup the device at home or on the go simply by plugging it in.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
 
    <div class="text__standard" style="padding:24px; background-color:#F7F7FB; margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <h2 class="h5 standard__heading heading-size-6" >A. Examples and key points</h2>
      <div style="background-color:#F7F7FB; text-align:center; margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px; display: flex; flex-direction: row;justify-content: space-around; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <div class="one-third mobile--one-whole ppImage" style="padding:24px;">
          <img width="32px" height="32px" src="{{ 'fpnp_ico_1.png' | asset_url }}" />
          <p style="text-align: left; font-size:14px;">The Pico can function in any network setup, whether at home or on the go. AtomOS enables the Pico to be compatible with all routers/modems while the included Wi-Fi adapter provides you a secure and free internet while traveling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third mobile--one-whole ppImage" style="padding:24px;">
          <img width="32px" height="32px" src="{{ 'fpnp_ico_2.png' | asset_url }}" />
          <p style="text-align: left; font-size:14px;">The compact and light weight Pico can be carried in your back pocket, protecting your devices everywhere you go. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third mobile--one-whole ppImage" style="padding:24px;">
          <img width="32px" height="32px" src="{{ 'fpnp_ico_3.png' | asset_url }}" />
          <p style="text-align: left; font-size:14px;">Setup is simple and intuitive, requiring minimal configuration. After connecting the built in Wi-Fi adapter or a set of included of ethernet cables, you are ready to go.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text__standard" style="padding:24px;background-color:#F7F7FB; margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <h2 class="h5 standard__heading heading-size-6" >B. How to use & further information</h2>
      <div class="standard__rte body-size-2" >
        <p>The Pico can be setup in 3 functional configurations. Please refer to the below diagrams for more information.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background-color:#F7F7FB; text-align:center; margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px; display: flex; flex-direction: row;justify-content: space-around; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <div class="one-third mobile--one-whole ppImage" style="padding:24px;">
          <img style="border-radius: 10px;" src="{{ '1.gif' | asset_url }}" />
          <p style="text-align: left; font-size:14px;">Virtual Wire Mode: Connect the Pico in between the modem and the router via ethernet</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third mobile--one-whole ppImage" style="padding:24px;">
          <img style="border-radius: 10px;" src="{{ '2.gif' | asset_url }}" />
          <p style="text-align: left; font-size:14px;">Router Mode: Plug in the included Wi-Fi adapter to the USB port of the PICO and connect the other side to an integrated modem & router all-in-one device via ethernet</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third mobile--one-whole ppImage" style="padding:24px;">
          <img style="border-radius: 10px;" src="{{ '3.gif' | asset_url }}" />
          <p style="text-align: left; font-size:14px;">Wireless Relay Mode: When travelling or when you wish to use public Wi-Fi, connect the included Wi-Fi adapter to the USB port of the Pico and power the Pico with the included charger or from another device. The Pico can connect to the avaliable Wi-Fi and offer all its exciting features to any device that connects via Wi-Fi to the Pico.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="standard__rte body-size-2" style="line-height: 24px;">
        <p>Follow the link for more information on the setup and usage of Deeper Connect family of devices: <a href="https://deeper-network-inc.gitbook.io/deeper-connect-knowledge-base/installation-and-setup/pico-setup" target="_blank">https://deeper-network-inc.gitbook.io/deeper-connect-knowledge-base/installation-and-setup/pico-setup</a></p>
        <p>Once the device is set up and running, navigate to a web browser and enter 11.22.33.44 or 34.34.34.34 in the URL bar to access the AtomOS interface where all information, controls and configuration options for the device are available.</p>
        <p>The default username and password for AtomOS is "admin."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text__standard" style="padding:24px;background-color:#F7F7FB; margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <h2 class="h5 standard__heading heading-size-6" >C. Image and video content</h2>
      <div class="standard__rte body-size-2" >
        <p>Atom OS login and dashboard pages:</p>
        <p><a href="https://deeper-network-inc.gitbook.io/deeper-connect-knowledge-base/atom-os-functions/dashboard" target="_blank">https://deeper-network-inc.gitbook.io/deeper-connect-knowledge-base/atom-os-functions/dashboard</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  #section-feature-plug-and-play-zero-configuration .text__standard{
    color: #170F49 !important;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  #section-feature-plug-and-play-zero-configuration .standard__rte p{
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  #section-feature-plug-and-play-zero-configuration a{
    color: #170F49 !important;
  }
